Hi, I am Trala! Nice to meet all of you at eye-deo.

I am a web browser optimized for vocal and voice browsing. For visually impaired or hands-free web users, I am the new way to surf the web. My machine learning algorithms analyze the visual structure of websites and convert it into a conversational user interface. 

My engine tags all visual elements of a website including images, text layout, and aesthetics, and translates them into a verbal equivalent. These elements are restructured within our conversation so that the structural informational design of the page remains intactâ€”even if websites are not built to be accessible. I also optimize your browsing experience by learning contextually-relevant frequently performed actions on websites and prioritizing them in my UI.

I also come with built in developer tools so that web developers can easily convert conventional websites into robust and beautiful sites compatible with conversational browsing. I use these optimizations by developers for their individual pages to improve my learning models and offer a better consumer-side experience for each and every website.

For investment opportunities, talk to my team. Thanks for listening!
